<br>
It was in the Amazon lands of Por Vida that Hope made her journey to secure mystical runes and burial markers for study. An enthusiastic plan not shared by the Scynthian Queen Alysia or Hope's very own daughter Kimbia. Alysia's loyal pets had surrounded Hope by a river. She had managed to keep them at bay, but Kimbia's arrival was unexpected. In the confrontation that followed, Hope had struck her head underwater and floated unconscious down the river.<br>
<br>
She had faint dreams of landing in another Amazon land, the Tanis River Valley region if her understanding of maps was accurate, but then she had lost consciousness once more. Something ... of a horse.. and a travel companion. Likely one of the Tanis River Amazons who took her to the nearest hospice. <br>
<br>
Hope stood from her bed, assuring a healer she would be well. She made her way from the hospice, outside to the small but well supplied town. With what money remained, she purchased a horse for the day. The owner had been generous considering the amount of gold dinars received. He gave Hope a couple days worth of small meal.<br>
<br>
Hope and her horse headed from the town at a steady, calm pace. On toward the nearest Amazon territory, the Amazon lands of Lesvos. She would reach their lands by nightfall, and with good fortune, convince the ruling elders there of her desire to learn the Amazon ways and traditions.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 355<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(6/6/02 10:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> No she wont</span><hr size=1> ~ Artemis appeared at the gates of the village, her hounds in line formation on either side of her. She had enough of this girl. Hope was getting nothing from Lesvos. She stood and waited for Hope to arrive.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxxdemeterxx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xxDemeterxx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(6/6/02 10:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Besides Artemis</span><hr size=1> ~*~ Demeter appeared in a burst of blue lights, standing besides Artemis, a smile on her lips. She had seen Hope try to kill a forest in Chadesia and did not like this one, one bit. She would stand besides Artemis and whoever else would stop this creature called Hope.~*~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonvelaska.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Velaska</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif" BORDER