&quot; I do not know Melousa, if you know of the being Hope. She is and immortal, who is up to something rotten. She had been caught in the other amazon lands, asking about our dead and artifacts from our dead. She has been to Themiscrya as well, but got nothing from the anceint City. Luckily, as do they, we do not bury our dead, but give them a proper amazon burial pyre. However, we ahve our sacred relics. Locked tightly away, guarded by magick that cannot be undone by evilness, nor cannot it not be undone by someone who was not born of amazon blood, such as Hope. We do not have much to worry about, but these are my lands and I will stand to protect them.&quot;<br>
~She explained then watched the dark forest around her, her night vision was like a jungle animals, perfect.~ <p>Queen Velaska of Lesvos Island
